{"tid":1009384,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"少年/成年 失智症討論","createTime":"2019-02-05T06:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:36.000Z","uid":80678,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"158746ecb727217043dc767decef849ce7ad8d85","tid":1009384,"uid":80678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"由19歲開始 到今年24<br />\n讀專上學院後<br />\n身邊朋友提醒自己 經歷完或者傾完某事<br />\n過一排自己可以完全無印象同無左件事<br />\n初時以為壓力大同分手 心情唔好<br />\n但依段時間 甚至覺得連細個的事都忘記左<br />\n<br />\n上堂 岩岩講完就唔記得<br />\n上星期 去完地方 得個圖像 但傾既野都已經好蒙糊<br />\n<br />\n已經不斷搵辦法改善同測試<br />\n網上個啲都無乜特別<br />\n<br />\n想知自己真係失智<br />\n定蠢 定有相同苦況的巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a2e1b99dca55c3638601266b31a53e3cf4f118","tid":1009384,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀專上學院？<br />\n<br />\nIve仔？<br />\n<br />\n算吧啦你"},{"pid":"df73ca2129d37ca85baf9f53a5210d7cc87a423f","tid":1009384,"uid":164932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"蠢 冇藥醫果隻"},{"pid":"60ab03eab4348249238f3cfe5c925a63a19a9aa9","tid":1009384,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"老人癡呆症就老人癡呆症, 咩失智症je"},{"pid":"d2ff045a9188c6c6e58dca578da697f9ae3d59ab","tid":1009384,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"弱智就弱智"},{"pid":"382b00d945ba6cbb88488788daa5a3bf6acb7243","tid":1009384,"uid":80678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"句句都串到應 不過你地都岩既"},{"pid":"99a81b4eb5477f643356a8a54472a5e0fffd5418","tid":1009384,"uid":150076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:46:01.000Z","msg":"返到工就無問題"},{"pid":"bd573392989ddd1cbffd93dac4b8773670ee9264","tid":1009384,"uid":114242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite